flowchart LR
    A[Joystick right] --> B[LFSR shift forward]
    A2[Joystick left] --> B2[LFSR shift backward]
    B --> C[New 8-bit state]
    B2 --> C
    C --> D[Decode bits: trees, obstacle, vine, treasure]
    D --> E[Render screen via TIA kernel]
    E --> F[Player sees jungle]

    style C fill:#cfe8d4,stroke:#2a7a3a,color:#000
    style D fill:#d6e0f5,stroke:#3a5aa2,color:#000
